title: NFC West QB-Commitment Index
description:
Nora and Mal discuss the NFC West and the different relationships and levels of commitment that the head coaches and organizations have with their quarterbacks (4:30). Then they answer a couple listener mail questions (50:15).

Hosts: Nora Princiotti and Mallory Rubin
Production Assistant: Isaiah Blakely
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
